&ldquo;Would you like to come to my house for a milk shake?&rdquo;
Until now, Emmanuelle had not noticed the girl who had leaped to her feet. But she was already amused by the expression of firmness and almost protective self-assurance of this new face-because it was also the face of a little girl.
Not so little, she corrected herself, as the adolescent standing before her seemed to take charge of her.
